                                <author>
                                    <persName ref="https://www.manuscripta.se/person/100481"> Birgitta Birgersdotter </persName>
                                </author>
                                <title type="desc">Revelations to the Popes</title>
                                <rubric>Iste Reuelaciones que sequuntur loquuntur de <add place="above">summis</add> pontificibus quas Alphonsus non omnes inseruit libris reuelacionum propter imminens scisma <gap reason="editorial"/> Et hanc reuelacionem portauit dominus hemmingus episcopus aboensis et frater petrus prior monasterii aluastra cisterciensis ordinis de regno Swecie. Capitulum primum.</rubric>
                                <incipit>Filius dei loquitur ad sponsam dicens Scribe ex parte mea pape Clementi verba hec</incipit>
                                <explicit defective="false">Verumptamen scias quod anima ista non est cum illis qui descendunt in infernum Nec cum illis qui veniunt ad grauiora examina purgatorii Sed cum illis qui quotidie festinanter appropinquant gracie et visioni maiestatis dei omnipotentis.</explicit>
                                <note>
                                    <p> The text stops in the middle of <locus from="59va" to="59va" scheme="folios"/>, after which a later hand has added the Swedish line <quote xml:lang="sv">herre hennes konglige man</quote>. The rest of the page is ruled, but no text.</p>
                                    <p>
                                        <locus from="60r" to="60v" scheme="folios"/>: ruled and with column numbers on 60r, but no text.</p>
                                </note>
                                <bibl>
                                    <title type="short" ref="https://www.manuscripta.se/bibl/107124">Jönsson (1997)</title>
                                </bibl>
