                                <title type="desc">Regula Salvatoris (The Birgittine rule)</title>
                                <rubric>Hic incipit Regula <add place="above">sancti</add> saluatoris data diuinitus ab ore christi deuotissime sponse sue domine byrgitte...</rubric>
                                <incipit>In dominio Regis noruegie qui est ad septentrionem </incipit>
