                                <locus from="94vb" to="98vb" scheme="folios"/>
                                <title type="uniform">Quattuor orationes</title>
                                <rubric>Iste oraciones subscripte fuerunt diuinitus reuelate beate B. de regno swecie In ista oracione a deo reuelata beate brigide deuote et pulcre laudatur gloriosa virgo maria de sancta concepcione et infancia sua. Et de omnibus virtuosis actibus et laboribus et magnis doloribus tocius vite sue et de sanctissima morte et assumpcione sua et cetera. </rubric>
                                <incipit>Benedicta et venerabilis Sis tu domina mea virgo maria dei mater sanctissima</incipit>
                                <explicit defective="false">Atque pro hiis qui in purgatorio per eam adiutorium et solamen habuerunt Qui viuis et regnas cum deo patre in vnitate spiritus sancti deus per omnia secula seculorum Amen</explicit>
                                <note>
                                    <p>
                                        <locus from="98vb" to="98vb" scheme="folios"/>: after the text three paragraphs by different hands have been added:</p>
                                    <p>
                                        <quote xml:lang="la">Post ortum domini christi regnantis <gap reason="editorial"/> In festo sancti quod contigit apolinaris</quote>
                                    </p>
                                    <p>
                                        <quote xml:lang="la">Hic designatur locus in quo carne soluta <gap reason="editorial"/> hanc incepta dies celestibus adnuncit apolinaris</quote>
                                    </p>
                                    <p>
                                        <quote xml:lang="la">Humilitas vestra est <gap reason="editorial"/> non sum dignus leuare oculos in celum</quote>
                                    </p>
                                    <p> The third paragraph has space reserved for an initial. Between the second and third paragraphs two words in brown ink have been erased (possibly <quote xml:lang="la">Hic designa</quote>).</p>
                                </note>
